metadata.name: Fading | 01
metadata.description:
This series was created as part of my ongoing project and solo exhibition dedicated to the beauty and wisdom of nature.

"Fading" is a collection of 10 1/1 digital photographs of dried Hydrangea in autumn, which shows how beautiful and important all life cycles are. 

Shot using vintage lens and macro extension tubes, edited in digital darkroom.
